                                 data-bs-parent="#accordionFaq">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    EquiBillBook updates automatically! Since it's a PWA, you'll always have the latest version without needing to download updates from app stores.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                                    What if I encounter installation issues?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive"
                                 data-bs-parent="#accordionFaq">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    If you experience any installation problems, please contact our support team. We're available 24/7 to help you get EquiBillBook up and running quickly.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSix">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-bs-target="#collapseSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                                    Which browsers support PWA installation?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSix"
                                 data-bs-parent="#accordionFaq">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    PWA installation is supported on most modern browsers including Chrome, Edge, Firefox, and Safari. The installation process may vary slightly between browsers, but all provide the same PWA experience.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSeven">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-bs-target="#collapseSeven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSeven">
                                    Can I use EquiBillBook on multiple devices?
