                            <div id="collapseSeven" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSeven"
                                 data-bs-parent="#accordionFaq">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    Absolutely! EquiBillBook works seamlessly across all your devices. Install it on your computer, phone, and tablet - all your data stays synchronized in real-time.
